<div class="section">





<section class="gpdc-section theme--lightAlt  ">
	<div>




    
    
    <div class="contentgrid">

	
	<div class="content-grid layout__1--c  ">
		
<div class="box ">
    




    
    
    <div class="textblock parbase">

 
 
   <div class="text-block         " data-ol-order-start="1" data-custom-mobile-width="false" data-custom-tablet-width="false" data-custom-desktop-width="false">
		<h4><a id="compat" rel="nofollow"></a>DUALSHOCK 4 wireless controller compatible games and applications</h4>
<p>You can use your wireless controller to play games streamed from your PS5™ console or PS4™ console to your compatible device using the PS Remote Play app.</p>
<p>Your wireless controller can also be used to play games that support DUALSHOCK 4 wireless controllers. </p>

	</div>

</div>


    
    
    <div class="buttonblock">

<div class="btn-block      " data-custom-mobile-width="false" data-custom-tablet-width="false" data-custom-desktop-width="false">
    <div>




    
    
    <div class="button">









    
        <a data-uuid="21a0916a-aa84-3472-8dc2-152cc08763f7" href="/en-us/support/games/playstation-remote-play-on-pc-and-mac/" class="text-link +iconized" role="button" target="_blank" target-tag="NONE|" data-dtm-label="PS Remote Play on PC and Mac" data-dtm-label-override="PS Remote Play on PC and Mac" data-age-gated="false" data-force-age-gate="false">
            <svg class="text-link__icon" viewBox="0 0 50 50" role="img" aria-label="Chevron right">
