    <div class="inlineAccordion">



   
<div class="accordion " data-component="accordion">
  
    <div>
      <a href="javascript:void(0);" id="accordion-section-1" data-item-title="accordion-section-1" class="accordion__item-title" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="sect1" rel="nofollow">
        <span class="link">Bluetooth limitations</span>
        <div class="chevron chevron-down icon-block">
          <svg class="" viewBox="0 0 50 50" role="img" aria-label="Chevron down">
            <use href="/etc.clientlibs/global_pdc/clientlibs/auto-clientlibs/pdc.designkit/resources/ps-icons-map.svg#ps-icon_chevron-down"></use>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="accordion__item-icons">
            </svg>
          <svg class="accordion__item-icon--plus" viewBox="0 0 50 50" role="img" aria-label="Open">
               <use href="/etc.clientlibs/global_pdc/clientlibs/auto-clientlibs/pdc.designkit/resources/ps-icons-map.svg#ps-icon_plus"></use>
            </svg>
            <svg class="accordion__item-icon--minus" viewBox="0 0 50 50" role="img" aria-label="Close">
               <use href="/etc.clientlibs/global_pdc/clientlibs/auto-clientlibs/pdc.designkit/resources/ps-icons-map.svg#ps-icon_minus"></use>
            </svg>
         </span>
      </a>
      <div data-item="accordion-section-1" class="accordion__item-description" role="region" aria-labeledby="accordion-section-1">
        
        <div>
          




    
    
    <div class="textblock parbase">

 
 
   <div class="text-block         " data-ol-order-start="1" data-custom-mobile-width="false" data-custom-tablet-width="false" data-custom-desktop-width="false">
		<p>If you are connecting a DUALSHOCK 4 wireless controller to a compatible Sony Xperia device, all functions are available. </p>
<p>For other devices, some wireless controller features are not available when connected via Bluetooth.</p>
<ul>
<li>Touchpad is not supported.<br />
</li>
<li>The color of the light bar cannot be changed. <br />
</li>
<li>Rumble, motion sensor, and headphone jack audio connection are not supported. <br />
</li>
</ul>

	</div>

</div>



        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
</div>

</div>



</div>
	</div>

</div>


