<div class="section">





<section class="gpdc-section theme--light  ">
	<div>




    
    
    <div class="contentgrid">

	
	<div class="content-grid layout__1--c  +thin-row-gap  +thin-col-gap  ">
		
<div class="box ">
    




    
    
    <div class="textblock parbase">

 
 
   <div class="text-block         " data-ol-order-start="1" data-custom-mobile-width="false" data-custom-tablet-width="false" data-custom-desktop-width="false">
		<h4><a id="reconnect" rel="nofollow"></a>Reconnect DUALSHOCK 4 wireless controller to your console</h4>
<p>To reconnect your wireless controller to your PS5 console or PS4 console, connect it with a compatible USB cable and press the PS button on the wireless controller. You can then remove the USB cable and use the controller wirelessly.</p>

	</div>

</div>



</div>
	</div>

</div>


</div>
</section>
