   <div class="text-block         " data-ol-order-start="1" data-custom-mobile-width="false" data-custom-tablet-width="false" data-custom-desktop-width="false">
		<h4><a id="issues" rel="nofollow"></a>Need more help with your DUALSHOCK 4 wireless controller?</h4>
<p>If you have followed the above instructions but believe your controller is not connecting properly, please visit the PlayStation Repairs diagnostic tool.</p>

	</div>

